  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "\n<p><b>Type:</b> Ninjutsu (Raiton)</p>\n<p><b>Rank:</b> 2 (Spell Level 1)</p>\n<p><b>Chakra Cost:</b> 6</p>\n\n<p><b>Learn DC:</b> 15 | <b>Successes:</b> 2</p>\n<p><b>Perform:</b> 3 | <b>Perform DC:</b> 15</p>\n\n<p><b>Components:</b> H</p>\n\n<hr>\n\n<p>You create a minor electric current in your Chakra pathways which can be focused, adding 1d4 electric damage to unarmed attacks or attacks with melee weapons, as long as there is a direct path of metal from where you touch the weapon to its striking surface (a sword, for example, would generally not be affected since you only hold it by its wood or leather grip).<br><br>You can also make unarmed touch attacks that deal 1d4 electric damage (not modified by Strength), but cannot score a critical hit. The technique remains active until you've made one attack per 2 levels (maximum 8 attacks). While active, you also receive a +1 bonus to Fortitude and Reflex saves against electric effects and techniques.</p>\n\n\n\n",
      "summary": "",
      "instructions": ""
    },
